title: Brasserie Sixty6
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, European, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Trendy modern European restaurant in Dublin 2. Has a separate veggie menu section. Staff reported to be attentive to dietary requests, and veggie items like risotto can be adapted to be vegan. May require booking for peak times. Free Wi-Fi and full bar.
